<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Well, I don't know much about faction or any other thing required to get this item. I have a little fourth lvl paladin i play when bored and he rarely kills anything that gives faction (orcs, fairies, gobs). Anyway, I tried this quest one night out of sheer boredom expecting to get nothing but exp, and on the first try i received it.  I gave it to my lvl 25 cleric right away and I love it. Best weapon I have ever used 1hb.  Do not sell it or trade it for ANY other weapon in the same price range. Granted, the very expensive 1hb weapons are better, but until I reach lvl 35 and I get a weapon out of kith forest, I plan on keeping it(BTW, if someone would let me loot a ruined or tainted battleworm morningstar out of kith forest, the weapon is theirs!) It is so gratifying to hit so fast that the mob's can only get a few hits off during the fight while you are wailing on them.  The damage is low (I max hit 13), but the speed and extra pluses more than make up for low damage. <BR>
<BR>
P.S. I play xegony with name bradenfor if someone would like to take me up on my offer mentioned above.  </font></td></tr></table>
