<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Verlok</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-04-25 14:14:39</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I got this hammer at lev 7 - after about 6 or 8 tries.  It is a rare drop - and faction doesn't affect it as long as it's not too low.<BR>
<BR>
The reason to get this in addition to a magic weapon (I'm a cleric - so I can summon one at 9th) is that it has a better damage ratio than any magic weapon you will likely be able to afford for another 10 or 20 levels.  In fact, it has one of the better damage ratios in the game, at least for clerics.  And the stat boosts don't hurt either.  And it's easy to get for a very low character - thus free.<BR>
<BR>
BTW - the loc from the last post for Red V is correct - him and his placeholders spawn on that spot, kill all the placeholders and he'll pop in about once every 3-5 times.  And you get the whatnots from the placeholders that you need for completing the box.</font></td></tr></table>
